### ==================== PHASE 5: TASK REMINDER EMAILS (Scheduled) ====================
### 
### 5.1 TASK REMINDER EMAIL - Due Soon Notification
### Email sent to: assignee's email
### Template: task-reminder.hbs
### Trigger: Scheduled job (typically 24 hours before due date)
### Includes: Task title, due date, priority, action link
### 
### How to test:
### 1. Create a task with dueDate = tomorrow
### 2. Manually trigger reminder (or wait for scheduled job)
### 3. Check email for notification
### 
### Example manual trigger would go here (if endpoint exposed):
### POST {{baseUrl}}/tasks/{{taskId}}/send-reminder
###


### ==================== PHASE 6: SECURITY & ALERT EMAILS (Future) ====================
### 
### 6.1 SECURITY ALERT EMAIL
### Template: security-alert.hbs
### Trigger: Suspicious login, password change, account modification
### Includes: Alert type, details, action required, support link
###


### ==================== EMAIL TESTING CHECKLIST ====================
###
### Before running tests:
### ☐ Verify .env has correct email credentials
### ☐ Confirm FRONTEND_URL is set correctly
### ☐ Check Gmail allows "Less Secure Apps" or using App Password
### ☐ Update email addresses in tests below
###
### After running tests:
### ☐ Check inbox for all expected emails
### ☐ Verify email content renders correctly (names, dates, links)
### ☐ Click all links in emails to verify they work
### ☐ Check for any errors in backend console logs
### ☐ Verify email footer has correct branding
### ☐ Test on mobile devices/email clients
###
### Email Verification Points:
### ✓ Recipient email is correct
### ✓ Subject line is clear and descriptive
### ✓ Sender name shows "Taska" or your brand
### ✓ All variables are populated (names, dates, titles)
### ✓ Action links point to correct URL
### ✓ Priority/urgency indicators are visible
### ✓ Email is mobile-responsive
### ✓ No broken images or styling issues
### ✓ Unsubscribe/footer links work
### ✓ No sensitive info exposed
###


### ==================== EXPECTED EMAIL FLOWS ====================
###
### 1. USER REGISTRATION FLOW:
###    Register → Welcome Email
###    ├─ User receives welcome email
###    ├─ Email contains login link
###    └─ User proceeds to login
###
### 2. PASSWORD RESET FLOW:
###    Forgot Password → Password Reset Email → Password Reset Success Email
###    ├─ User receives OTP email (4 min expiry)
###    ├─ User enters OTP + new password
###    └─ User receives confirmation email
###
### 3. TASK ASSIGNMENT FLOW:
###    Task Created → Task Assigned Email → [Task Updates?] → Task Completed Email
###    ├─ Admin creates task for user
###    ├─ Email sent to assignee with details
###    ├─ User completes task
###    └─ Celebratory email sent to user
###
### 4. TASK REMINDER FLOW (Scheduled):
###    Task Due Soon → Task Reminder Email
###    ├─ Scheduled job runs 24h before due date
###    ├─ Reminder email sent to assignee
###    └─ User takes action
###


### ==================== EMAIL TEMPLATE REFERENCE ====================
###
### Template Files Location: src/mail/templates/
###
### Available Templates:
### • welcome.hbs
###   └─ Triggered: User registration
###   └─ Contains: Welcome message, role info, portal link
###
### • password-reset.hbs
###   └─ Triggered: Forgot password request
###   └─ Contains: OTP code, expiry time (4 min), support link
###
### • password-reset-success.hbs
###   └─ Triggered: Password successfully reset
###   └─ Contains: Confirmation, reset time, security notice
###
### • task-assigned.hbs
###   └─ Triggered: Task created for user
###   └─ Contains: Task title, description, due date, priority, portal link
###
### • task-completed.hbs
###   └─ Triggered: Task marked as completed
###   └─ Contains: Congratulations message, task name, completion date
###
### • task-reminder.hbs
###   └─ Triggered: 24 hours before due date
###   └─ Contains: Task title, due date, priority, action link
###
### • login-notification.hbs
###   └─ Triggered: User logs in (if enabled)
###   └─ Contains: Login time, IP address, device info
###
### • security-alert.hbs
###   └─ Triggered: Security events
###   └─ Contains: Alert type, details, action required
###


### ==================== DEBUGGING EMAIL ISSUES ====================
###
### Issue: "Emails not sending"
### Solution:
### 1. Check backend logs for error messages
### 2. Verify .env credentials are correct
### 3. Confirm Gmail account settings (Less Secure Apps enabled)
### 4. Check network connectivity
### 5. Verify MAIL_HOST and MAIL_USER are correct
###
### Issue: "Template not rendering properly"
### Solution:
### 1. Verify .hbs file exists in src/mail/templates/
### 2. Check for syntax errors in template
### 3. Verify all context variables are passed
### 4. Check email client CSS support
###
### Issue: "Emails going to spam"
### Solution:
### 1. Check email headers (SPF, DKIM, DMARC)
### 2. Add unsubscribe link to footer
### 3. Verify sender credentials
### 4. Use branded domain for sending
### 5. Check email content for spam triggers
###
### Issue: "Some variables show as [undefined]"
### Solution:
### 1. Verify context object is passed correctly
### 2. Check template variable names match context keys
### 3. Add null checks in template ({{#if variable}})
### 4. Log context object being passed
###
